<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Role Change Request</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="background-color: #f8f8f8; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <h1 style="color: #4a4a4a; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 10px;">Role Change
            Request Received</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">Dear <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50;">
                <%= userName %>
            </span>,</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">We have received your request to change your role to <span
                style="font-weight: bold; color: #3498db;">
                <%= requestedRole %>
            </span>. Our admin team will review your request and get back to you shortly.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px;">Thank you for your patience.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><span
                style="font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50;">Plana Team</span></p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #777;">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Plana. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>